### Create Customer - Retail Customer (triggers CustomerCreatedEvent)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/crm/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-123-4567",
  "customerType": "RETAIL",
  "tenantId": "tenant-001"
}

